channel.description:
Care about free speech? Tired of political correctness? Like discussions about big ideas? Watch Dave Rubin on The Rubin Report. Real conversations, unfiltered rants, and one on one interviews with some of the most interesting names in news and entertainment. Comedians, authors, and influencers join Dave each week to break down the latest in politics and current events. Real people, real issues, real talk.

The Rubin Report is a show in three parts:

► Direct Message: Dave offers a voice of reason on the most relevant and important issues. Unfiltered, unapologetic, speaking directly to you.

► The Sit Down: Dave goes one on one with some of the biggest names in news and entertainment.

► The Panel: A talk show about the biggest topics and ideas in the news featuring two outspoken guests.

The Rubin Report is available on Ora TV, right here on YouTube, on Roku, and as a podcast.

Click below to subscribe!
